00:31:11.000 --> 00:31:14.630
And I'd say, see if you
can settle your attention

00:31:14.630 --> 00:31:16.840
on the feeling of
the breath, just

00:31:16.840 --> 00:31:21.000
the normal, natural breath,
however it's appearing for you.

00:31:21.000 --> 00:31:24.050
You don't have to try to
make it deeper or different.

00:31:24.050 --> 00:31:26.480
And watch your
mind at the moment

00:31:26.480 --> 00:31:30.860
that you realize you're thinking
about dinner or your vacation

00:31:30.860 --> 00:31:31.790
or whatever it is.

00:31:34.900 --> 00:31:37.890
See how you speak to yourself.

00:31:37.890 --> 00:31:40.260
And if that is a
pretty harsh voice--

00:31:40.260 --> 00:31:42.786
kind of punitive or belittling--

00:31:42.786 --> 00:31:46.340
you can recognize that.

00:31:46.340 --> 00:31:50.990
See if you can
soften that response.

00:31:50.990 --> 00:31:54.040
Remember that our goal is to
just let go and begin again.

00:31:54.040 --> 00:31:55.930
If you have to do that
billions of times,

00:31:55.930 --> 00:31:57.611
that doesn't mean
you're doing it wrong.

00:31:57.611 --> 00:31:58.360
You're doing fine.

00:32:02.390 --> 00:32:03.960
OK, so you can
just find the place

00:32:03.960 --> 00:32:07.890
where the breath is clearest
for you or strongest for you.

00:32:07.890 --> 00:32:12.352
Maybe that's the nostrils,
or the chest, or the abdomen.

00:32:12.352 --> 00:32:14.060
Bring your attention
there and just rest.

00:32:19.640 --> 00:32:20.990
See if you can feel one breath.

00:32:40.620 --> 00:32:42.900
Remember, the most
important moment

00:32:42.900 --> 00:32:46.237
is the moment after
you've been distracted,

00:32:46.237 --> 00:32:47.195
after you've been lost.

00:33:18.030 --> 00:33:20.760
No matter how many times you may
have to let go and begin again,

00:33:20.760 --> 00:33:22.125
it's not a problem.

00:33:22.125 --> 00:33:23.250
That's the point, actually.

